quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  7,82,"Jaabawol yim…ìe makko …ìen e pankare makke on ko …óuurnagol wi'a : "Yaltinee Luuti e yim…ìe mun …ìen ka ho…óo mo'on ; kam…ìe ko …ìe la…ì…ìintinotoo…ìe e kuu…óe amen, …ìe haanaa heddodude e amen"."
  7,83,"Men hisindini mo e yim…ìe makko …ìen tuma Men yamirnoo …ìe yaltirgol ho…óo ngo lepte …óen yanata e mun ngon jemma, si wanaa debbo makko on ; o heddoduno e yim…ìe leptaa…ìe …ìen."
  7,84,"Men saa∆¥ini to…ìo tii…óungo e ma…ì…ìe, tuma Men weddinoo …ìe kaa∆¥e loope, Men wayliti ho…óo ngon, Men wa…ótiri dow on ley. Teskee an Nulaa…óo, honno battane yim…ìe Luuti bom…ìe …ìen laatornoo? ∆äen battane ko halkaare e koyeera wonnoo."
  7,85,"Men Nulii kadi faade e le√±ol Madyana ngol, si…ó…óo ma…ì…ìe on Su'aybu (yo o hsi), o maakani …ìe : "Ko onon yo yim…ìe am, rewee Alla tun. Hanndu…óo e reweede alanaa on si wanaa Kanko. Gom…óii …ìanngannduyee arii on immorde ka Alla, wonnde ko mi goongu…óo. ∆äum non, tottiree haqqeeji yim…ìe …ìen timminirangol …ìe etir…óe …óen e manndakke …óen, wata on …óuytiran …ìe "sil'a" ma…ì…ìe on fii ko aybi, maa janfo…óon …ìe e …óum. Wata on bonnir ka leydi keeferaaku e geddi …ìaawo ndi mo∆¥∆¥inireede immineede Annabaa…ìe adinoo…ìe. Ko …óum moo…óon …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥annde on si on laatike gom…óim…ìe"."
  7,86,"Wata on joo…óo e kala laawol, hi…óon kammbana fe∆¥∆¥oo…ìe ngol, ja…ìon jawle ma…ì…ìe, sakko…óon …ìe e laawol peewal, hi…óon …óa…ì…ìana laawol Alla ngol kadi oo√±aare fii wata yim…ìe …ìen jokku ngol. Annditee neema Alla on e mo'on yetton Mo ; o laatinoke see…óaa…ìe O …óu…ó…óini on. Taskee honno battane bonnoo…ìe …ìen ado mon laatornoo, …óum ko halkaare e jirbugol wonnoo."
  7,87,"Si tawii fedde e moo…óon gom…óinii kon ko mi addi immorde ka Joomi am, fedde goo gom…óinaali …óum, haray hadditee onon …ìee fennoo…ìe, kon ko Alla senndirta hakkunde mon. Ko Kanko …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥ude e √±aawoo…ìe sennda …ìen."